data.description: Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough. Welcome home! Boasting a full paint refresh and brand new carpeting throughout, this home offers a fresh and inviting ambiance. As you enter, you'll be greeted by an open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area that seamlessly flows together. The expansive layout provides ample room for various furniture arrangements, allowing you to design the space to suit your personal taste. The fully equipped kitchen features sleek dark cabinets, elegant quartz countertops, and gas cooking. The large breakfast bar serves as a hub for casual dining and additional meal prep space. Tucked away for ultimate privacy, the primary suite is situated in a split layout and comes complete with its own ensuite bathroom. Step outside to discover a generously sized fenced backyard that presents a blank canvas for new owners. And with no rear neighbors, you'll enjoy an added layer of privacy as you enjoy the outdoors. Don't miss it!
